      <h2 class="mb-3">About Us</h2>
     <p class="font-weight-bold">Purpose:</p>
      <p>The Caring Hearts Foundation is dedicated to making a positive impact on the lives of individuals and communities in need. Our mission is to provide support, resources, and opportunities to improve the well-being and quality of life for those facing various challenges.</p>
     <p class="font-weight-bold">Core Values:</p>
     <p>1. Compassion:<p> We believe in showing empathy, care, and understanding towards individuals and communities in difficult circumstances.</p>
      <p>2. Empowerment: We strive to empower individuals by providing them with the necessary tools, education, and support to overcome challenges and build a better future.</p>
      <p>3. Collaboration: We foster partnerships and collaborations with other organizations, stakeholders, and volunteers to maximize our collective impact and create sustainable change.</p>
      <p>4. Integrity: We operate with honesty, transparency, and accountability in all our actions and decision-making processes.</p>
      <p>5. Social Justice: We are committed to promoting equality, fairness, and social justice for all, irrespective of their background or circumstances.</p>
